STATE EX REL. DEWINE
v.
OMAR IBN EL KHATTAB MOSQUE, INC. 2017-1067 Supreme Court of Ohio. January 22, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENTS

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

On appellant's motion for leave to amend certificate of service and request for additional response time. Motion granted. Appellee may file a response to the motion for reconsideration within ten days.
